ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:
This project is based on the face-recognition-attendance system by Prince Singh Rathore
(https://github.com/Prince9193/face-recognition-attendance) and includes significant
enhancements and modifications for academic purposes as part of the SEU Pattern 
Classification course project.

Key enhancements include:
- Triple face detection mechanism (HOG → CNN → Enhanced)
- Multi-photo attendance with automatic deduplication
- Optimized recognition threshold (0.42) for classroom scenarios
- Comprehensive evaluation tools and testing framework
- Enhanced database schema and CRUD operations
